dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Dylan Phillips. May I please have your name?
Hello, my name is Cheryl Gray.
Nice to meet you, Cheryl. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it is five six two three eight nine.
Thank you, Cheryl. Can you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, it is December fourteenth nineteen eighty-two.
Great, thank you for confirming. How can I assist you today with your auto insurance policy?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle.
Thank you for your time, Cheryl. I have successfully added the new vehicle to your policy. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you, Dylan, for your help.
You're welcome, Cheryl. Have a great day!
